  "response": "Finding a reliable solar panel installation provider in Anderson, CA, involves considering several factors such as experience, customer reviews, certifications, and warranties. Here are some providers you might consider:\n\n1. **Hes Solar** - Known for excellent customer service and high-quality installations.\n2. **SunPower by Hooked on Solar** - Offers high-efficiency solar panels and has a solid reputation.\n3. **Sunrun** - One of the largest solar companies in the U.S. with flexible financing options.\n4. **SolarCity (now part of Tesla)** - Provides reliable products and services with advanced technology.\n5. **Vivint Solar** - Offers a variety of solar plans and transparent pricing.\n\nAlways ensure to check for updated reviews, request quotes, and compare services before making a decision. Local companies might also offer more personalized service, so it's worth looking into regional providers as well.",
